'''民都洛水牛'''（[[学名|学名]]：''{{lang|la|Bubalus mindorensis}}''），又名'''塔摩洛水牛'''、'''菲律賓水牛'''、'''棉蘭老水牛'''或'''明多羅水牛'''，是一種細小的[[水牛|水牛]]。<ref name="ITISBM">{{ITIS | ID = 625123 | taxon = Bubalus mindorensis | year = 2007 | date = 17 March}}</ref>牠們是[[菲律賓|菲律賓]][[民都洛|民都洛]]的[[特有種|特有種]]，且是菲律賓內唯一的[[牛科|牛科]]。一般相信牠們也曾在[[呂宋|呂宋]]出沒。牠們原先分佈在整個民都洛，由海邊至[[海拔|海拔]]2000米以上的山區，但因[[人類|人類]]的發展及獵殺，現只限於一些偏遠的草原，且是[[瀕危物種|瀕危物種]]。<ref name=IUCN/>

與一般信念及以往分類不同，民都洛水牛並非[[沼澤水牛|沼澤水牛]]或[[水牛|水牛]]的[[亞種|亞種]]。民都洛水牛較沼澤水牛多毛，面上有較淺色的斑紋，角較短，且不是群居的。<ref name="haribon">{{cite web | last =Fuentes | first =Art | title =The Tamaraw: Mindoro's endangered treasure | work =Haribon | publisher =Haribon Foundation for the Conservation of Natural Resources | date =2005-02-21 | url =http://www.haribon.org.ph/index.php?q=node/view/130&PHPSESSID=f07b7a39774972130ec811e029e12f5d | accessdate =2007-03-17 | archive-date =2007-09-27 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20070927184137/http://www.haribon.org.ph/index.php?q=node%2Fview%2F130&PHPSESSID=f07b7a39774972130ec811e029e12f5d | dead-url =no }}</ref>牠們是菲律賓內最大的本土陸上[[動物|動物]]。

== 形態 ==
民都洛水牛的外表是典型的[[牛科|牛科]]。牠們的身體短壯，四肢有蹄，頭細小而有角，[[頸部|頸部]]短小。牠們較[[水牛|水牛]]細小的壯實。牠們只有輕度的[[兩性異形|兩性異形]]：雄牛的頸較粗。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.wildcattleconservation.org/SpeciesFactSheets/bubalus-mindorensis.htm |title=Tamaraw ''bubalus mindorensis'' Heude, 1888 |accessdate=2007-07-12 |author=Wild Cattle Conservation |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071008173448/http://www.wildcattleconservation.org/SpeciesFactSheets/bubalus-mindorensis.htm |archive-date=2007-10-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>平均肩高100-105厘米，體長220厘米，尾巴長60厘米。雌牛估計重200-300公斤。

成牛的毛色呈深褐色至灰色。蹄及前下肢內側有白色斑紋，形狀像[[山地倭水牛|山地倭水牛]]的斑紋。面部顏色像身體，大部份在[[眼睛|眼睛]]至角上有一對灰白色斑紋。鼻子及嘴唇有黑色的[[皮膚|皮膚]]。[[耳朵|耳朵]]長13.5厘米，內側有白紋。

民都洛水牛的角短而呈黑色，兩角成丫形，而非像水牛的彎月形。兩角的表面扁平，底部呈[[三角形|三角形]]。由於經常磨擦，民都洛水牛的角外表面磨損，而內表面則粗糙。角長35.5-51厘米。<ref name="UltimateUngulate">{{cite web | last =Huffman | first =Brent | title =''Bubalus mindorensis'': Tamaraw | work =www.ultimateungulate.com | publisher =Ultimate Ungulate.com | date =2007-01-02 | url =http://www.ultimateungulate.com/Artiodactyla/Bubalus_mindorensis.html | format =html | accessdate =2007-03-17 | archive-date =2007-02-10 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20070210131707/http://www.ultimateungulate.com/Artiodactyla/Bubalus_mindorensis.html | dead-url =no }}</ref>

== 分佈及棲息地 ==
民都洛水牛最初是於1888年在[[民都洛|民都洛]]發現的。由於[[瘧疾|瘧疾]]肆虐，於1900年前，民都洛並不多人居住。直至發明了抗瘧疾的[[藥物|藥物]]後，才有較多的人遷到島上居住。[[人類|人類]]活動在島上的增加減少了民都洛水牛的數量。到了1966年，民都洛水牛的分佈地就只餘下三個地區；到了2000年，牠們只能在餘下的兩個地區生活。<ref name="AnimalInfo">{{cite web | last =Massicot | first =Paul | title =Animal Info - Tamaraw | publisher =Animal Info | date =2005-03-05 | url =http://www.animalinfo.org/species/artiperi/bubamind.htm | format =htm | accessdate =2007-03-18 | archive-date =2007-03-04 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20070304021613/http://www.animalinfo.org/species/artiperi/bubamind.htm | dead-url =no }}</ref>

於1900年代估計民都洛水牛的數量有約10000頭；到了1949年，牠們的數量就有約1000頭；於1953年，就只有少於250頭仍然存活。<ref name="OryxKuehn1977">{{cite journal en | last =Kuehn | first =David W.| title =Increase in the tamaraw | journal =Oryx | volume =13 | issue = | pages =453 pp. | year =1977| id = ISSN: 0030-6053 / EISSN: 1365-3008}}</ref>[[世界自然保護聯盟|世界自然保護聯盟]]的統計發現牠們的數量不斷下降，只餘下少於100頭。<ref name="IUCN1969">{{cite book en | author=International Union for the Conservation of Nature and Natural Resources | title =1969 IUCN 1969 Red Data Book. Vol. 1 - Mammalia | publisher =IUCN | year =1969 | location =Morges, Switzerland}}</ref>於1975年就稍稍回升至120頭。<ref name="Oryx1989d">{{cite journal en | title =Major effort to save the tamaraw | url =https://archive.org/details/sim_oryx_1989-07_23_3/page/126 | journal =Oryx | volume =23 | pages =126 pp. | year =1989 | id = ISSN: 0030-6053 / EISSN: 1365-3008}}</ref>現時相信牠們只餘下約30-200頭。<ref name=IUCN/>

民都洛水牛只生存在[[民都洛|民都洛]]，加上在其他島上發現的[[水牛屬|水牛屬]][[化石|化石]]，顯示牠們曾一度廣泛分佈在[[菲律賓|菲律賓]]。<ref name="Croft2006">{{cite journal en | last =Croft | first =Darin A. | coauthors =Lawrence R. Heaney, John J. Flynn, Angel P. Bautista | title =Fossil remains of a new, diminutive ''Bubalus'' (Artiodactyla: Bovidae: Bovini) from Cebu island, Philippines | journal =Journal of Mammalogy | volume =87 | issue =5 | pages =1037 | publisher =American Society of Mammalogists | date =03-08-2006 | url =http://www.bioone.org/perlserv/?request=get-abstract&doi=10.1644%2F06-MAMM-A-018R.1 | doi =10.1644/06-MAMM-A-018R.1 | accessdate =2007-03-17 | archive-date =2021-09-05 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20210905131542/https://bioone.org/journals/journal-of-mammalogy/volume-87/issue-5/06-MAMM-A-018R.1/FOSSIL-REMAINS-OF-A-NEW-DIMINUTIVE-BUBALUS-ARTIODACTYLA--BOVIDAE/10.1644/06-MAMM-A-018R.1.full | dead-url =no }}</ref><ref name="Burton2005">{{cite journal en | last =Burton | first =J. A. | coauthors =S. Hedges, A. H. Mustari | title =The taxonomic status, distribution and conservation of the lowland anoa ''Bubalus depressicornis'' and mountain anoa ''Bubalus quarlesi'' | journal =Mammal Review | volume =35 | issue =1 | pages =25-50 | publisher = | year =2005 | url =http://www.blackwell-synergy.com/doi/abs/10.1111/j.1365-2907.2005.00048.x?journalCode=mam | doi =10.1111/j.1365-2907.2005.00048.x | accessdate =2007-03-17 }}{{Dead link|date=2019年10月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>根據20世紀發現的化石紀錄，民都洛水牛曾於[[更新世|更新世]]在[[呂宋|呂宋]]生活。<ref name="Beyer1957">{{cite journal en | last =Beyer | first =H. O. | title =New finds of fossil mammals from the Pleistocene strata of the Philippines | journal =Bulletin of the National Research Council of the Philippines | volume =41 | pages =220-238 | publisher =National Research Council of the Philippines | year =1957}}</ref>

民都洛水牛喜歡棲息在[[熱帶|熱帶]]的高地[[森林|森林]]。牠們會在厚叢林及近開放的林間帶覓食，主要是吃[[草|草]]及[[竹|竹]]為生。由於[[人類|人類]]的開發，牠們擴展至棲息在低地的[[草原|草原]]。牠們很多時都會在水源不遠處出沒。<ref name=IUCN/><ref name="AnimalInfo"/>

== 食性 ==
民都洛水牛主要吃[[草|草]]及嫩[[竹|竹]]，也會吃[[白茅|白茅]]及[[甜根子草|甜根子草]]。牠們天生是日間活動的，但因要避開[[人類|人類]]，也會轉到晚上才活動。<ref name="haribon"/>

== 生命周期 ==
民都洛水牛一般壽命為20歲，最高可達25歲。牠們每胎會產一子，[[妊娠期|妊娠期]]為300天。<ref>[http://genomics.senescence.info/species/entry.php?species=Bubalus_mindorensis Ageing, longevity, and life history of Bubalus mindorensis] {{Wayback|url=http://genomics.senescence.info/species/entry.php?species=Bubalus_mindorensis |date=20100212033211 }}. Accessed March 5, 2007</ref>每胎要相隔兩年。幼牛會由母牛照顧2-4年才能獨立。<ref name="haribon"/>

== 行為 ==
民都洛水牛是獨居的，並不會以群族聚居。只有幼牛才會表現出一般[[水牛|水牛]]的群族行為及階級。<ref name="Kuehn1986">{{cite journal en | last =Kuehn | first =David W. | title =Population and Social Characteristics of the Tamarao (''Bubalus mindorensis'') | journal =Biotropica | volume =18 | issue =3 | pages =263-266 | url =http://links.jstor.org/sici?sici=0006-3606(198609)18%3A3%3C263%3APASCOT%3E2.0.CO%3B2-C#abstract | doi =10.2307/2388495 | accessdate =2007-03-17 | date =Sep 1986 | archive-date =2021-09-05 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20210905131532/https://www.jstor.org/stable/2388495#abstract | dead-url =no }}</ref>雄牛及雌牛全年也會接觸，但只會有幾小時。有指牠們的獨居行為是對其[[森林|森林]]棲息地的一種適應性。<ref name="haribon"/>雄牛很多時是獨居，且似乎帶有攻擊性；雌牛則可以獨居、與雄牛或與三頭不同年齡的幼牛同住。<ref name="Walker 1">{{cite book en |last=Nowak |first=Ronald M. |title=Walker's Mammals of the World |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=7W-DGRILSBoC&pg=PA1149&dq=tamaraw+solitary&sig=WIQZJ3tj64zpLDMkLoPnyNL890E |year=1999 |publisher=JHU Press |isbn=0801857899 |pages=1149}}</ref>

民都洛水牛像其他的[[牛科|牛科]]般會在泥坑中打滾，這可能是為避免[[昆蟲|昆蟲]]咬傷。<ref name="McMillan2000">{{cite journal en | last =McMillan | first =Brock R. | coauthors =Michael R. Cottam, Donald W. Kaufman | title =Wallowing Behavior of American Bison (''Bos bison'') in Tallgrass Prairie: An Examination of Alternate Explanations | journal =American Midland Naturalist | volume =144 | issue =1 | pages =159-167 | publisher =The University of Notre Dame | url =http://links.jstor.org/sici?sici=0003-0031%28200007%29144%3A1%3C159%3AWBOAB%28%3E2.0.CO%3B2-O&size=LARGE | accessdate =2007-03-17 | date =July 2000 | archive-date =2021-09-05 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20210905131532/https://www.jstor.org/stable/3083019 | dead-url =no }}</ref>民都洛水牛生性兇猛，不過所有的資料卻很有限。牠們在受威脅時，會低下頭，以角相向，且會不斷搖頭。<ref name="UltimateUngulate"/>

== 命名及分類 ==
民都洛水牛最初被[[法國|法國]][[動物學|動物學家]][[韓伯祿|韓伯祿]]（Pierre Marie Heude）於1888年分類為[[倭水牛|倭水牛]]的一種。牠們與[[水牛|水牛]]的親密關係已被確認，於1958年被分類為[[水牛|水牛]]的[[亞種|亞種]]。<ref name="Bohlken1958">{{cite journal en | last =Bohlken | first =H. | title =Vergleichende Untersuchungen an Wildrinden (Tribus Bovini Simpson, 1945) | journal =Zoologische Jahrb cher (Physiologie) | volume =68 | pages =113-202 | year =1958}}</ref>[[基因|基因]]分析亦支持這種親密關係。<ref name="Wall1992">{{cite journal en | last =Wall | first =David A. | coauthors =Scott K. Davis, Bruce M. Read | title =Phylogenetic Relationships in the Subfamily Bovinae (Mammalia: Artiodactyla) Based on Ribosomal DNA | journal =Journal of Mammalogy | volume =73 | issue =2 | pages =262-275 | publisher =American Society of Mammalogists | url =http://links.jstor.org/sici?sici=0022-2372(199205)73:2%3C262:PRITSB%3E2.0.CO;2-I | doi =10.2307/1382056 | accessdate =2007-03-17 | date =May 1992 | archive-date =2021-09-05 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20210905131535/https://www.jstor.org/stable/1382056 | dead-url =no }}</ref>於1969年，牠們被提升為獨立的[[物種|物種]]。<ref name="Groves1969">{{cite journal en | last =Groves | first =C. P. | title =Systematics of the ''Anoa'' (Mammalia, Bovidae) | journal =Beaufortia | volume =223 | pages =1-12 | year =1969}}</ref>

後來發現倭水牛應為[[水牛屬|水牛屬]]的一部份，故此民都洛水牛的學名亦有所更改。<ref name="MSWBM">{{cite web | title ='''Bubalus mindorensis''' | work =Mammal Species of the World (MSW) | publisher =Smithsonian National Museum of Natural History | year =1993 | url =http://nmnhgoph.si.edu/cgi-bin/wdb/msw/names/query/14224 | accessdate =2007-03-17 | deadurl =yes | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/19961019003222/http://nmnhgoph.si.edu/cgi-bin/wdb/msw/names/query/14224 | archivedate =1996-10-19 }}</ref>

== 保育 ==
民都洛水牛的數量稀少，且只生存在[[民都洛|民都洛]]，故被列為[[極危物種|極危物種]]。<ref name=IUCN/>牠們的分佈地[[面積|面積]]少於500平方公里，且已知只有五個位點。<ref name=IUCN/>有很多原因導致民都洛水牛的衰落。[[人類|人類]]在民都洛的發展使民都洛水牛的數量受到壓力，加上獵殺及烹食，且失去棲息地的情況下數量大幅下降。另外於1930年代，入侵的[[歐洲牛|歐洲牛]]引發了嚴重的[[牛疫|牛疫]]，同時令民都洛水牛也受到感染。牠們於2007年時的數量就少於300頭。<ref name=IUCN/><ref name="haribon"/>

因民都洛水牛的衰落，[[菲律賓|菲律賓]]有[[法律|法律]]及機構來保育牠們。法律上包括禁止除自衛外的獵殺及傷及民都洛水牛，懲罰具阻嚇性的罰款及監禁。<ref name="CA73">{{cite web | title =An act to prohibiting the killing, hunting, wounding or taking away of ''Bubalus mindorensis'', commonly known as tamaraw | work =Commonwealth Act No. 73 | publisher =National Assembly of the Philippines | date =1936-10-23 | url =http://www.lawphil.net/statutes/comacts/ca_73_1936.html | format =html | accessdate =2007-03-18 | archive-date =2007-06-26 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20070626230919/http://www.lawphil.net/statutes/comacts/ca_73_1936.html | dead-url =no }}</ref>除了法律禁止外，多項的保育工作也在進行，包括飼養及培育民都洛水牛及建立[[基因池|基因池]]。於2007年，民都洛水牛被列在《[[瀕危野生動植物種國際貿易公約|瀕危野生動植物種國際貿易公約]]》的附錄一，任何民都洛水牛及其衍生物的商業貿易都被禁止。<ref name="CITESAPP">{{cite web|author=CITES |title=Appendices |work= |publisher=Convention on International Trade in Endangered Species of Wild Flora and Fauna |date=2007-05-03 |url=http://www.cites.org/eng/app/appendices.shtml |format=shtml |accessdate=2007-08-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070203100154/http://www.cites.org/eng/app/appendices.shtml |archivedate=2007-02-03 }}</ref><ref name="CITES">{{cite web|author=UNEP-WCMC |title=Bubalus mindorensis |work=UNEP-WCMC Species Database: CITES-Listed Species |publisher=United Nations Environment Programme - World Conservation Monitoring Centre |date= |url=http://sea.unep-wcmc.org/isdb/CITES/Taxonomy/tax-species-result.cfm?displaylanguage=eng&Genus=Bubalus&Species=mindorensis&source=animals&Country=PH |id=A-119.009.004.003 |accessdate=2007-08-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070930204524/http://sea.unep-wcmc.org/isdb/CITES/Taxonomy/tax-species-result.cfm?displaylanguage=eng&Genus=Bubalus&Species=mindorensis&source=animals&Country=PH |archivedate=2007-09-30 }}</ref>

